{
  "stem": "22836.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And finally, I was waiting into the night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was waiting to late in the night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we have-- we have a signal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "If somebody get lost or something, and-- and look-- to come in one place to meet each other.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Then I-- I went to the place to meet you all-- who is-- maybe somebody survive-- come to the place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "When I come to the place, I couldn't get in, in that place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I say, something wrong.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "In that place was a man live with a Jewish girl, in Osowa.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And-- and he promise-- he promise.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So he-- she gonna survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He gonna-- and she's-- I was coming there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And she says to me, Louis, I have to die.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I say-- I say nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "This is life.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You've got to survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "She was leave with him in the night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And she even get pregnant from him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he was keep on the day there, in the back, in a room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ukraine and Jewish girl-- Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, well, he was good to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was-- we can trust him, because if you figure.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I come to him-- and I couldn't-- I'm afraid to get in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know what I'm-- and then I get in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I get him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he says, that-- there was your-- the-- the police.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they kill that girl, and they want to kill him, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I say, I'm-- I'm in bad shape.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I run away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I run away, and I see nobody is there-- nobody there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When I come tomorrow, I went to another friend, to a-- to Ukrainians, and find out what going on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He wouldn't kill me, never.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He's very good-- Maxime.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a good friend for all the time there, when I been a mate.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
